2007-09-28  TSUCHIYA Masatoshi  <tsuchiya@namazu.org>

	* shimbun.el (toplevel): Add a new slot `url-coding-system' to
	`shimbun' class.
	(shimbun-retrieve-url): Accept an argument `url-coding-system', which
	specifiies the coding system for escaping non-ASCII characters included
	in the given URL.
	(shimbun-fetch-url): Refer the above slot when calling
	`shimbun-retrieve-url'.
	(shimbun-mime-replace-image-tags): Add an argument `shimbun' to use
	`shimbun-fetch-url' instead of `shimbun-retrieve-url'.
	(shimbun-make-mime-article): Follow the above change.

	* sb-multi.el (shimbun-multi-retrieve-next-pages): Follow the above
	change.

