	* shimbun.el: Changes to handle <BASE> tag properly.
	(shimbun-make-mime-article): Accept a base URL of this current article
	as the 3rd optional argument.
	(shimbun-current-base-url): New function.
	(shimbun-make-html-contents): Call the above.
	(shimbun-from-address): Accept backends that have no address.

	* sb-multi.el: New virtual class.

	* sb-atmarkit.el: Use `shimbun-multi' class.
	(shimbun-multi-next-url, shimbun-multi-clear-contents): New methods.
	(shimbun-atmarkit-use-base-url): Abolished.
	(shimbun-article-url, shimbun-make-contents): Cancel the last change,
	because `shimbun-multi' class handles <BASE> tag properly.
	(shimbun-atmarkit-from-address): Abolished.

