2005-07-03  Tsuyoshi CHO  <tsuyoshi_cho@ybb.ne.jp>

	* sb-cnn-jp.el (shimbun-cnn-jp-prefer-text-plain): Add new variable,
	set as text type.

	* sb-engadget-ja.el: New file.

2005-07-02  David Hansen  <david.hansen@physik.fu-berlin.de>

	* sb-heise.el: (shimbun-heise-wash-telepolis-article): Remove more ads.

2005-06-28  TSUCHIYA Masatoshi  <tsuchiya@namazu.org>

	* nnshimbun.el: Changes to support an ephemeral group.
	(TOPLEVEL): Add autoloads for `gnus-group-prefixed-name' and
	`gnus-kill-ephemeral-group'.
	(nnshimbun-group-prefixed-name): Accept an optional argument, `server'.
	(nnshimbun-group-ephemeral-p): Use the above function.
	(nnshimbun-request-group): Ignore `dont-check' argument when requesting
	an ephemeral group.
	(nnshimbun-close-group): Close a NOV buffer for an ephemeral group.
	(gnus-group-make-shimbun-group): Use a prefixed name as an ephemeral
	group.  Kill an ephemeral group before making it an ordinary group.

2005-06-26  Andreas Seltenreich  <seltenreich@gmx.de>

	* sb-zeit-de.el (shimbun-get-headers): Append "?page=all" to the URLs
	to get complete articles again.

