	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal; use
	shimbun-content-end instead of shimbun-content-end-internal.

	* sb-yahoo-sports.el: Don't inherit shimbun-text, which was mis-applied
	and ineffective.

	* sb-yahoo.el (shimbun-yahoo-prefer-text-plain): Default to nil so as
	to generate html articles as before.

	* sb-zeit-de.el (shimbun-make-contents): Use shimbun-content-start
	instead of shimbun-content-start-internal; use shimbun-content-end
	instead of shimbun-content-end-internal.

