	(shimbun-wiki-group-alist): Add optional 4th and 5th elements to each
	inner list.  Add doc string.
	(shimbun-headers): New method.
	(shimbun-make-contents): Ditto.
	(shimbun-rss-build-message-id): Modify regexp to support Hiki.  Build
	message-id without string `rss'.
	(shimbun-index-url): Pick up URL from shimbun-wiki-group-alist and
	simply return it.
	(shimbun-wiki-group-alist): Modify ADDRESS of hiki.
	(shimbun-rss-build-message-id): Modify message-id format.

	* sb-rss.el (shimbun-rss-get-encoding): Bug fixed.  Return interned
	encoding with suffix `-dos'.
	(shimbun-headers): Simplified.

