	* sb-text.el (shimbun-shallow-rendering): Use defun instead of
	defsubst.

	* sb-asahi.el: Autoload sb-text instead of always to require the
	feature.
	(shimbun-asahi-make-contents): Make an article in the text/plain
	format.
	* sb-asahi-html.el (shimbun-asahi-html-make-contents): New function
	moved from sb-asahi.el.

	* sb-yomiuri.el: Autoload sb-text instead of always to require the
	feature.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-make-contents): Make an article in the text/plain
	format.
	* sb-yomiuri-html.el (shimbun-yomiuri-html-make-contents): New function
	moved from sb-yomiuri.el.

