	* mew-shimbun.el (mew-shimbun-retrieve-article)
	(mew-shimbun-re-retrieve-article): Sort headers by the date.

	* sb-slashdot-jp.el
	(shimbun-slashdot-jp-parse-date-string): `12PM' means noon.  '12AM'
	means at night.

2002-03-01  Yuuichi Teranishi  <teranisi@gohome.org>

	* sb-lump.el (shimbun-lump): Add `check-interval'.
	(shimbun-lump-check-interval): New inline function.
	(shimbun-lump-check-p): Use it.

2002-03-01  TSUCHIYA Masatoshi  <tsuchiya@namazu.org>

	* sb-slashdot-jp.el (shimbun-slashdot-jp-story-count): New internal
	constant.
	(shimbun-slashdot-jp-make-headers): The action when range is not set is
	changed.  Search old stories.
	(shimbun-index-url): Removed.
	(shimbun-slashdot-jp-make-story-headers): Change argument spec.  Refer
	the above constant to decide the URL of the index page.
	(shimbun-slashdot-jp-search-comment-head): Ignore a garbage line
	between author and date.

2002-03-01  TSUCHIYA Masatoshi  <tsuchiya@namazu.org>

	* sb-lump.el (shimbun-get-group-header-alist): Add the 2nd optional
	argument.
	(shimbun-headers): Call the above function with the 2nd argument.

	* sb-wired.el (shimbun-get-group-header-alist): Ignore the 2nd optional
	argument.

	* sb-slashdot-jp.el: Inherit sb-lump.el.
	(shimbun-headers): Abolished.
	(shimbun-get-group-header-alist): New method.
	(shimbun-slashdot-jp-make-headers): New function.

	* sb-slashdot-jp.el (shimbun-make-contents): Bind `case-fold-search' to
	t locally.
	(shimbun-headers): Ditto.

