2001-10-15  NAKAJIMA Mikio  <minakaji@osaka.email.ne.jp>

	* sb-fml.el (shimbun-get-headers): Call `shimbun-retrieve-url' with arg
	NO-DECODE when CODING-SYSTEM is non-nil.  Call `shimbun-retrieve-url'
	with arg RELOAD.  Set enable-multibyte-characters to t and decode
	region according to CODING-SYSTEM when CODING-SYSTEM is non-nil.

	* sb-w3m-dev.el (shimbun-w3m-dev-coding-system): New variable.

	* shimbun.el (shimbun-retrieve-url): Reindent.  Set
	enable-multibyte-characters to nil when NO-DECODE is non-nil.

