	* sb-asahi.el (shimbun-asahi-x-face-alist): New variable.

	* sb-zdnet.el (shimbun-zdnet-x-face-alist): Ditto.

	* sb-wired.el (shimbun-wired-x-face-alist): Ditto.

	* sb-cnet.el (shimbun-cnet-x-face-alist): Ditto.

